      <h2 class="h2">Commentary</h2>
      <div class="note album-overview-copy">
        <p>“Traffic Lights” is a song that has been years in the making. It is a song I had wanted to write for a long time, but I didn’t know how to put the words to paper. It tells a story of growing up, feeling stuck and unsure of yourself, while recognising that, as a person, you are constantly changing and evolving, and that no one is one-dimensional.</p>

        <p>The instrumental is heavily influenced by one of my favourite songs, “Supercut” by Lorde. It is a very electronic, synth-led song that is catchy and memorable, but at first listen you do not realise the heaviness and symbolism of the lyrics. That is something I tried to achieve with my own song.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

